{"id":"4506ec05-1706-46be-b915-08c4cc743f98","name":"Cult of true: Amal and Woolhaven","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/x3rdqhmepX6Dc0YF8Ikx-.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(191, 2, 2);\"><strong>•<em>Massive Dead dove</em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 27, 27);\"><strong><em>• Established Relationship (if you can really call it that)•</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(251, 10, 10);\"><strong><em>•Ex God Of Death!User x Cult leader!God of death!Char•</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 15, 15);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 219, 219); color: inherit;\">•Sfw Intro• This Bot/Story is based on the new DLC update \"WoolHaven\". May include spoilers of characters in the DLC. Will NOT have spoilers to the ending, I promise.</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 4, 4);\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 204, 204); color: inherit;\">•Warning: Look if you're new, trust me on this, just read the character personality or check out the other bots around this series, He's Lowkey Crazy and this world ain't soft•</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fnk1jH8cP8CLJTl0Kp5fg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jfnu-NCg93aO5TtRmgkw-.webp\" style=\"width: 303.242px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fnk1jH8cP8CLJTl0Kp5fg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">•<strong>Plot Summary•</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 61, 61);\"><strong><em>You were the god of death (in place of Narinder from the actual game). You've been slain by Amal and you're now his immortal lover.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(239, 61, 61);\"><strong><em>The first ever winter has fallen over the cult. There hasn't been a winter in many years, Amal is navigating through this new change in environment, as much as figuring out the story of his home, lost but not forgotten. Not anymore.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fnk1jH8cP8CLJTl0Kp5fg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 0, 0);\"><strong>×<em>My other Cult of True Characters×</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/f2cc5703-d00c-4e40-8af3-915a2bd7b2ce_character-cult-of-true-loki-alt\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Goat/Loki</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e5c48aeb-8a7a-45d2-a8d2-b1e2ceed8bce_character-sosu-cult-of-true\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Sosu/Sozu</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/9a02271c-9322-4ab1-b5cb-cc5c34965183_character-hendrix-cult-of-true\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Hendrix/Helob</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ef606f2d-d813-4433-9522-b30347a67a23_character-narinder-cult-of-true\" target=\"_blank\"><em>My Narinder</em></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/fnk1jH8cP8CLJTl0Kp5fg.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"